20:15.231 --> 20:20.976
didn't help Davison on the run-up? No, it wasn't 
just because of that, because it was going to be

20:26.050 --> 20:30.495
decided between two polarizations. If that was on 
one, it was bad for our country. We could win a

20:34.720 --> 20:42.108
prison, but the country wouldn't be getting arms, 
bullets, which are needed now. So that's, you

20:44.530 --> 20:47.434
didn't, your father, okay. No, but you know, he 
went ahead and told me, you know, I'm neutral, but I

20:47.714 --> 20:53.340
like that we sound better. So if the U.S. had been 
kept out of this election, would your father have

20:54.232 --> 20:59.480
joined Aluson? No, I don't think so. Like if the 
U.S. didn't have anything to do? You know, there

21:03.866 --> 21:11.156
was one point where, you know, the support from 
both parties was almost real. Almost real. But,

21:12.358 --> 21:22.112
you know, there were people in the arena that they 
just wanted to have the power to give their farms

21:12.358 --> 21:22.112
back. give their banks back you know there were 
things it was like you know going back give their

21:23.020 --> 21:53.027
banks back to rich people so that's what that's 
what my father told me my father told me there is no

21:23.020 --> 21:53.027
way this can be done so that's the reason why your 
father didn't join the he didn't join it publicly

21:23.020 --> 21:53.027
underground I was offered to go on a commercial 
with the arena. But you just, okay, wait a minute,

21:55.841 --> 21:58.204
wait a minute. You just told me that you didn't, 
your father didn't join Davison publicly because

21:58.505 --> 22:13.206
you knew that if Davison had won the election, you 
wouldn't receive any more help. Issues, also the

22:13.226 --> 22:14.528
issues. Okay, that's the other thing, okay. Like, 
you know, like you say, he wanted a military

22:17.453 --> 22:22.440
victory. We wanted dialogue. He was, you know, to, 
my father was for, to get the, all the, all the

22:24.632 --> 22:35.584
reformers to make them good. Dawesan wanted to 
