22:50.585 --> 22:51.547
and the issues. And the issues. But Duarte is not, 
you know, what you're hearing here. He's not? He's

22:57.836 --> 23:02.864
not, because, you know, I was with him at, you know, 
we met with both parties. But usually with the PDC,

23:04.266 --> 23:09.775
with Duarte's party, we just had an hour or 
something like that. But with that we saw, you see,

23:11.240 --> 23:14.803
we always ended up, you know, until next day. Ah, I 
see. You know, here I read, like, I thought it was, I

